<h2>The stuff I've done</h2>

<p>This is a gallerie of some of my current and past side projects. Some need polishing, some are not finished and some don't work the way I'd want but it's a good ego boost to keep a list of things I have achieved.</p>

<div class="projects-board">
    {% for project in projects %}
    <div class="project-card">
        {% set usedURL = project.demo_url or project.article_url or project.code_url or '#' %}
        <a href="{{usedURL}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img class="project-img" src="../{{project.image}}""/>
        </a>
        <div class="text-overlay">
            <a href="{{usedURL}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <h3 class="project-title">{{project.name}}</h3>
            </a>
            <p>{{project.description}}</p>
            <p>
                {% if project.demo_url %}
                <a href="{{project.demo_url}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Demo</a>
                {% if project.code_url %} - {% endif %}
                {% endif %}

                {% if project.code_url %}
                <a href="{{project.code_url}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Code</a>
                {% if project.article_url %} - {% endif %}
                {% endif %}

                {% if project.article_url %}
                <a href="{{project.article_url}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Article</a>
                {% endif %}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
</div>
